@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!-- Page Header Start -->
<div class="container-fluid page-header py-6 my-6 mt-0 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-white animated slideInDown mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb animated slideInDown">
            <ol class="breadcrumb justify-content-center mb-0">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a class="text-white" href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a class="text-white" href="#">F.A.Q</a></li>
            </ol>
        </nav>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Page Header End -->
<!-- Faq Section Start -->
<div id="rs-faq" class="rs-faq pt-5 md-pt-90" style="padding-bottom: 35px;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="sec-title2 mb-45">
                    <span class="sub-text style-bg"><b>F.A.Qs</b></span>
                    <h2 class="title title6">Do You Have Any Questions?</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <div id="accordion" class="accordion">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true">Who is Bivisoft ?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Bivisoft offers software development services, software development team outsourcing, and software training.
                                        Its a registered company in the United Kingdom with the company number
                                        13890545 and Nigeria with the RC-1767781.
                                    </p>
                                    <br />
                                    <p>
                                        Currently,they have setup a 15months software internship programme where they train passionate people from
                                        novice to intermediate software developers. The Internship programme is divided into <b> Bivisoft Training </b>
                                        and <b> Bivisoft Fellowship.</b>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false">What's Bivisoft Training?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Bivisoft Training is a 3months training where we train people with zero programming experience and
                                        teach them starting from scratch on HTML, CSS, JavaScript, JQuery, C#, ASP.NET Core and SQL Server .
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false">What's Bivisoft Fellowship ?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Bivisoft Fellowship is a 12months programme where students that passed the Bivisoft Training will be accepted in and
                                        merged in software teams where they will work together with our inhouse experienced software engineers working in complex
                                        softwares that solve everyday problems.
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        During the fellowships our interns get the opportunity to use professional software development tools, work together with
                                        experienced developers who do code reviews, get access to connect external mentors who are working with most Nigerian banks
                                        and International companies.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsefour" aria-expanded="false"> Why should I Apply for Bivisoft’s Internship Program?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapsefour" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        If you desire to start a career in tech, upskill or you would just like an opportunity to work with global companies
                                        and get a high-paying job in fifteen months, then the Bivisoft training program is for you.
                                        Our 15-month intensive training combines a world-class curriculum with real-life projects to get you ready for your dream job.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsefive" aria-expanded="false"> Who can apply to be a bivisoft Intern?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapsefive" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>To become a member of the bivisoft fellowship  you must meet up with the following requirements:</p>
                                    <br />
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>The applicant must be a graduate who has completed the NYSC program, currently looking for a place of primary assignment or not going for NYSC</li>
                                        <li>The applicant must provide two grantors.</li>
                                        <li>The applicant can't be a student currently Schooling.</li>
                                        <li>The applicant grantors' must provide an updated post cheque of <b> N1,200,000 </b></li>
                                        <li>The applicant will provide originals of their BSC certificate</li>
                                        <li>Must be available in the office 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday throughout the 15months of the internship.</li>
                                        <li>Must be computer literate & tech-savvy.</li>
                                        <li>Must Have a little coding experience in HTML,CSS & JavaScript.</li>
                                        <li>Must have a good laptop with at least 8GB Ram and i5 processor.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false">  What's the total internship duration?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseSix" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        The internship will take 15 months which are broken down as follow;
                                        fellowship runs for twelve months while training runs for three months.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false">
                                    How much will the fellowship and training cost?
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseSeven" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p class="">
                                        The cost of the internship is N1,200,000 and the students will only pay after the internship when we have connected
                                        them to our partner companies who are always stand-by to hire our graduates.
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        The only money the student pays upfront is the agreement fee of N30,000 which goes into the preparation
                                        of the contracts between the student and Bivisoft Limited.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false">  Where is your office located in Enugu?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseEight" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Our office is located at No 19B Church Street, Enugu East, Enugu
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false">  Do you have accommodation for your trainee?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseNine" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Yes, there is accommodation at students' own cost.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <a class="card-link collapsed" href="#" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTen" aria-expanded="false">  How can I Apply?</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseTen" class="collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordion" style="">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>
                                        You can apply through the link below:
                                        <br />
                                        <a asp-controller="Accounts" asp-action="Application" class="btn btn-primary py-2 w-25 mt-3 px-lg-5 d-none d-lg-block" style="border-radius: 15px">Apply Here</a>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>